com.example.meditrackr.models

Class Patient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.meditrackr.models.Profile
      • com.example.meditrackr.models.Patient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Patient
extends Profile
implements java.io.Serializable
    Patient: A Patient has a list of problems which can be retrieved. Problem objects can be added or deleted from the list, and the list can be checked to see if a particular problem exists in the list. A Patient also has all the information associated with the Profile class, including username, email, and phone.
